            <div class="why-check-badge" aria-hidden="true">✔</div>
            <div class="why-card-text">
              <h3>Experienced Professionals</h3>
              <p>Our licensed clinical team, led by Dr. Oyebisi, possesses decades of combined expertise in restorative, surgical, and preventative care.</p>
