              <p>We believe in detailing options. The doctor maps out a dental plan, guiding you through procedures step-by-step to eliminate anxiety.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Card 4: Flexible booking -->
          <div class="why-card reveal-scale stagger-4">
            <div class="why-check-badge" aria-hidden="true">✔</div>
